snippet.title: Dunk City Dynasty Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Attention all basketball enthusiasts! The Dunk City Dynasty will soon be available for Android users on Philippines on March 29th, so don't miss out on this ballin' party!  
Unleash your inner baller with all-stars in a variety of competitive modes. Build your squad, challenge other players, and light up the court!
Pre-download the game now and be one of the first to hit the court! You can download the game from either Google Play Store or our official website in the Philippines. 
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.netease.dunkcd&gl=ph
Official Website: https://www.dunkcitymobile.com/
